  "description": "Biomechanical Morphus tables. Table I: Dark Designs pp. 138–139; Core pp. 106–107. Table II: Dark Designs pp. 140–141; Between the Shadows pp. 132–133 (roll Table I, II, or mix). Table III: Nightbane Survival Guide pp. 83–85. Components are living Morphus tissue—not cybernetic prosthetics—and heal at the Nightbane’s normal rate. In most cases, Disguise, Seduction, and Undercover Ops are impossible (Table II repeats this note).",
